    "description": "本游戏能够在Steam Deck上完美运行。<br><br>《飞雷喵》是一款2D平台探索解谜游戏，玩家的主要能力是跟飞镖交换位置的飞雷「哔」之术，并会随着游玩过程得到更多「需要消音」的能力。<br><br>特征<br>- 多人游戏模式（2-4 位玩家）与好友合作或竞赛<br>- 容易学习，难以掌握<br>- 充满神秘色彩的故事<br>- 没有战斗<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276600/extras/3e6141d09967404da4726b4caf90f7fc.poster.avif?t=1741569727\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276600/extras/3e6141d09967404da4726b4caf90f7fc.webm?t=1741569727\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276600/extras/3e6141d09967404da4726b4caf90f7fc.mp4?t=1741569727\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>完全通关须时：4小时<br><br>作为一款well-like游戏，我们提供：<br>- 用玩家的创造力解决平台难题，大多数地方都有不只一种解决方案<br>- 以不同的顺序收集能力能带来不同的游戏体验<br>- 如果玩家对游戏有足够的理解，过关效率会难以置信地高<br>- 奖励在指定游戏时间内通关游戏的玩家<br>- 动物（开玩笑）<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276600/extras/91a8c893afa2f5f54a3f7de93ac32edf.poster.avif?t=1741569727\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276600/extras/91a8c893afa2f5f54a3f7de93ac32edf.webm?t=1741569727\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276600/extras/91a8c893afa2f5f54a3f7de93ac32edf.mp4?t=1741569727\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>但很遗憾，我们没有：<br>- 需要硬核玩家社群一起破解的谜题<br>- 头目战<br>- 华丽的粒子效果<br>- 超细的游戏容量<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276600/extras/84a4b192220ded9f9695794fabb44b97.poster.avif?t=1741569727\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276600/extras/84a4b192220ded9f9695794fabb44b97.webm?t=1741569727\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276600/extras/84a4b192220ded9f9695794fabb44b97.mp4?t=1741569727\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>假如你喜欢这款作品，务必要去玩玩《动物井》。",
